  "3328880": {
    "name": "Block Number 5",
    "steam_appid": 3328880,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328880/extras/7378f23e466bf2c2cd1cc2b28b7bd214.poster.avif?t=1737889142\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328880/extras/7378f23e466bf2c2cd1cc2b28b7bd214.webm?t=1737889142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BN5 是最真实的涂鸦视频游戏。我们是嘻哈文化的一部分，这款游戏的每个角落都充满了来自全球涂鸦作家的真实艺术作品。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328880/extras/3dfdffeb91ee7015558172009e8a1d6a.poster.avif?t=1737889142\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328880/extras/3dfdffeb91ee7015558172009e8a1d6a.webm?t=1737889142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过混合字母、字符、符号，甚至你最喜爱的涂鸦传奇人物的作品，创造属于你自己的独特涂鸦风格。你的风格选择将决定世界如何看待你和你的艺术。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328880/extras/e3e7cc8bc2f722334b97944db431c16d.poster.avif?t=1737889142\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328880/extras/e3e7cc8bc2f722334b97944db431c16d.webm?t=1737889142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>金字塔是一座乌托邦式的城市，分为 4 个区块，都在强权压迫者的统治之下。由于城市是垂直建造的，高楼甚至会偷走低楼的阳光。从地下下水道到最高的屋顶，探索这些街区并给它们贴上标签......但要小心警察！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328880/extras/11f8b40588cfe4f4cd144e8ed4dea4cb.poster.avif?t=1737889142\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328880/extras/11f8b40588cfe4f4cd144e8ed4dea4cb.webm?t=1737889142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>整个城市都是你的画布，你可以在任何地方涂鸦！但请记住，你并不是唯一的街头涂鸦者。涂鸦王们声名远播，备受尊敬，他们不会让你轻易夺走他们的王冠。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328880/extras/0c2bbf038c4af84be61dc547b1aada61.poster.avif?t=1737889142\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328880/extras/0c2bbf038c4af84be61dc547b1aada61.webm?t=1737889142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的道路掌握在自己手中：是成为著名的街头艺术家，还是臭名昭著的涂鸦破坏者？在《金字塔》中，你将根据自己的风格、所到的地点和所做的叙述选择为自己正名。</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 简体中文, 繁体中文, 韩语, 日语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 泰语, 土耳其语, 乌克兰语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
